  "name": "RPlog_Spiran_Rescue",
  "title": "The Iriaz Island Rescue",
  "summary": "On the tropical island world near Spira, the Sith Admiral Crestian Tarasar assembles a five-strong strike team to rescue two captive children, Shen and Rahasia, from Trandoshan raiders. The team, including the young Sith apprentice Kipran Jawatha, his mother Moff Elana Tracer, the Zeltron Councillor Sha Dark, the droid Commander V1C3, and the embedded reporter Jordaan Mag, are ferried by the fisherman Nat Pagle and slip ashore at an unguarded eastern entrance. Using Kipran's Force-sense of the children and Crestian's slicing skill, they infiltrate the estate, evade and then eliminate Trandoshan patrols, and extract first Shen and then Rahasia in a tense, mostly silent operation that erupts into a brief firefight. Crestian is knocked down and has his ribs cracked by a charging raider before killing the lizard with a dagger, but the team withdraws with both children unharmed. The party reaches the boat and departs, the mission a quiet success leaving only dead Trandoshans behind, the rescued siblings reunited.",
